Oligonucleotides were obtained from Shanghai Sangon Biotechnology Co., Ltd. (China). The sequence of oligonucleotides are as follows:


Hairpin DNA (HD): 5′- CAT CTC TTC TCC GAG CCG GTC GAA ATA GTG AGT ATA CCA GCT TAT TCA ATT AAG AGA TG-3′;



Substrate Chain: 5′- ACT CAC TAT rA GGA AGA GATG-MB-3′;



Auxiliary DNA (AD): 5′- CAT CTC TTCC-3′.
